iêu Minh thái tử phân kinh thạch đài - 梁昭明太子分經石臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Sinh-d%C3%A2n-6/poem-ZRfh1YIuOMT2RSUoKDc40g">Sinh dân 6 - 生民 6</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Ti%C3%AAu-dao-du-ph%C3%BA/poem-rpyThlh2WwqoWCZR7lnYbg">Tiêu dao du phú - 逍遙遊賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-t8ceGQaUvFAomirH_IzMQg">Xuất dương - 出洋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-H7U7KCvecgO1KzCd1kGc9A">Phan Thanh Giản</a>)<br></div>	</div>
